Text:
A great magazine, thanks!
Unfortunately, it hasn't been available in my area for several years.
I got the November-2010 issue from Demonoid,
but do you have January-October 2010, and maybe all of 2009 and 2008?
It would be great if you or another TPB member could up these.
Or even a complete mega-collection!
Again, thanks for sharing this!
